The paper deals with the multiple-input multiple-output (MIMO) broadcast channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of statistical channel state information (CSI) is also a common theme in communication networks (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses an iterative algorithm and a low complexity transmission scheme, which are topics in machine learning (cs.LG) and optimization (cs.MM).
